      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Secret Ingredient",
        "Client": "Yomogi the Chef",
        "Description": "So my idea is to make these\r\nnew Bunny Dango that\u0027ll\r\nrefresh you just like a power\r\nnap would. But to do that, I need\r\nyou to capture a \u003CCOL RED\u003ESomnacanth\u003C/COL\u003E\r\nso I can use its song to make\r\na recipe! I love you and please!",
        "Target": "Capture a Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, time expires,\r\nor capture target slain"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "L\u0027ingr\u00E9dient secret",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "J\u0027aimerais pr\u00E9parer des dango\r\nqui puissent te revigorer\r\ncomme une bonne sieste. Mais\r\npour \u00E7a, il va falloir que tu\r\nme captures un \u003CCOLS RED\u003ESomnacanth\u003C/COL\u003E.\r\nJ\u0027ai besoin de son chant pour\r\nma recette ! S\u0027il te pla\u00EEt ?",
        "Target": "Capturer un Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9\r\nCible tu\u00E9e"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "L\u0027ingrediente segreto",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "Vorrei creare dei nuovi dango\r\na coniglietto che mettano\r\nin forze quanto un sonnellino,\r\nma ho bisogno che mi catturi\r\nun \u003CCOLS RED\u003ESomnacanth\u003C/COL\u003E, cos\u00EC potr\u00F2\r\nusare la sua canzone per la\r\nricetta. Grazie, ti adoro!",
        "Target": "Cattura un Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero, tempo scaduto\r\no mostro da catturare ucciso"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Die Geheimzutat",
        "Client": "Yomogi die K\u00F6chin",
        "Description": "Ich will neue Dango kreieren,\r\ndie genauso belebend sind wie\r\nein Nickerchen. Deshalb m\u00F6chte\r\nich dich bitten, einen\r\n\u003CCOLS RED\u003ESomnacanth\u003C/COL\u003E zu fangen, damit\r\nich sein Lied f\u00FCr das Rezept\r\nverwenden kann! Bitte!",
        "Target": "Fange einen Somnacanth.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0, Zeit l\u00E4uft ab\r\noder Fangziel erlegt."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "El ingrediente secreto",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "Hay quien dice que el canto\r\ndel \u003CCOLS RED\u003ESomnacanth\u003C/COL\u003E hace dormir.\r\nSi lo usase como inspiraci\u00F3n,\r\n\u00A1podr\u00EDa hacer dango que\r\nsentasen como una relajante\r\nsiesta! \u00BFPodr\u00EDas capturarme\r\nuno?",
        "Target": "Captura un Somnacanth",
